rows.label: xs08110100_MSG0003
rows.name:
Hmph. She's scared.
Let's start with her first.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08110100_MSG0004
rows.name:
Lin, calm down.
Remember the battles we've fought so far.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08110100_MSG0005
rows.name:
Have we ever faced something we couldn't handle?
It's okay. We're with you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08110100_SEL0011
rows.name: Nod silently, indicating you will definitely win.

rows.label: xs08110100_SEL0021
rows.name: Reach out your hand to run away together.

rows.label: xs08110100_MSG0008
rows.name: I feel like I can do it if I'm with you all![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08110100_MSG0009
rows.name:
Thank you.
For doing that for me...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08110100_MSG0010
rows.name:
But we can't run away.
We have to protect the city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08110100_MSG0011
rows.name: Sorry, I lost my head for a second.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08110100_MSG0012
rows.name:
I'm okay now.
Let's take 'em down![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08110100_MSG0013
rows.name:
Hmph. Looks like we've got someone bossy here.
She must be the commander, eh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08110100_MSG0014
rows.name:
Hey Dagahn, take her down!
Charge![ST:wait ]
